Class TrialManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.rocketapp.controller.TrialManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockTrialManager

    public class TrialManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that handles adding, retrieving, and modifying experiment trials from firestore. Singleton with static methods for convenience.

      • listen

        public static void listen(Experiment experiment,
                          ObjectCallback<Experiment> onUpdate)
        Listens to firestore for changes to this experiment. You MUST use this to get the trials for an experiment. You may want to update the UI in onUpdate.
        Parameters:
        experiment - The experiment to listen to.
        onUpdate - Callback for implementing desired behaviour when the experiment is updated in firestore.
